class Solution(object):
    def maxScore(self, nums, x):
        """
        :type nums: List[int]
        :type x: int
        :rtype: int
        """
        total_score = sum(nums)
        n = len(nums)
        min_loss = float('inf')
        left, current_loss = 0, 0
        target = total_score - x
        
        if target == 0:
            return total_score
        
        for right in range(n):
            current_loss += nums[right]
            while current_loss > target and left <= right:
                current_loss -= nums[left]
                left += 1
            if current_loss == target:
                min_loss = min(min_loss, right - left + 1)
        
        if min_loss == float('inf'):
            return -1
        
        return total_score - min_loss
